Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.40,0:24:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}塔奇克马式的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.45,0:24:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人围殴才干掉的对手我怎么可能打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.57,0:24:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.50,0:24:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 好像眼泪流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.81,0:25:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.44,0:25:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙好像不动耶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.81,0:25:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.70,0:25:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 动起来了


